The South African Weather Service has issued a weather warning of strong winds heavy rain and snow.Key routes are being monitored said the province s MEC for Co-operative Governance and Traditional Affairs Nomusa Dube-Ncube."We appeal to all [people] to avoid crossing rivers or streams because we have lost many lives in the past when people attempted [walk or drive] crossing a river or a low-lying bridge " said Dube-Ncube.